OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe odd
OL,6,Flight shower is possible at first.
OL,7,FOtherwise, dry with clear spells and
OL,8,Flight winds. This will allow
OL,9,Ftemperatures to fall away and a patchy
OL,10,Ffrost to form.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry, bright and chilly
OL,13,Fstart. Remaining mostly dry with cloud
OL,14,Fincreasing from the west. Some light
OL,15,Frain is possible in the west by
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
