OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FShowers
OL,6,Fpossible on Sunday. Cloudy on Monday
OL,7,Fwith further showers and longer spells
OL,8,Fof rain later. Turning rather wet and
OL,9,Fwindy on Tuesday. Temperatures slowly
OL,10,Fincreasing near to average.
